Author: Chibi-Bunny
Text: I just wanted to say I relate. Even at my lowest, in the hospital, I felt fake and like I was way too big. You're not alone, good luck

Author: sashavelwhore
Text: As someone with anxiety and an ED, feeling fake is one of the top symptoms. But don't let that dissuade you from doing what's best for your health. Every time you get that inkling feeling that you won't be taken seriously because you aren't severe enough, remember that that's your anxiety and ED speaking, NOT a universal fact.  Sending good vibes your way, love.
